Output demo/forgen-demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Type "# Install forgen globally"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "npm install -g forgen"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "# Initialize your philosophy"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "forgen onboarding"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "# Check your environment"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "forgen doctor"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "# Start Claude Code with your philosophy"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "forgen"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "# That's it! Your principles now drive your workflow."
Enter
Sleep 2s
